snippet.title: "NEEDY STREAMER OVERLOAD" PlayStation 5 / PlayStation 4 Release Date Announcement PV
snippet.description:
The PlayStation 5 / PlayStation 4 version of "NEEDY STREAMER OVERLOAD" is set to launch on January 21, 2025!

Additionally, the "NEEDY STREAMER OVERLOAD: Internet Angel Pack" will be released on Steam on the same day, January 21, 2025!

This special bundle includes the main game along with newly produced spin-off content, an artbook, and the second volume of the soundtrack, making it a fantastic deal for fans!
